---
source: src/compiler/orm/tests/explain_tests.rs
expression: "explain_select(SelectOperation::List, \"Org\", &inc, &plan)"
---
SELECT PLAN (LIST) `Org` · 3 stages · 5 steps
INCLUDE
└─ `board`
   ├─ `banner`
   ├─ `entries`
   └─ `top`

STAGE 0
└─ SCAN `Org` ON d1 `db` LIMIT `$limit` MANY

STAGE 1
├─ SCAN `Board` ON durable `BoardDo` INTO `board` ONE
│     JOIN `parent.tenantId` = `row.tenantId`
│     SHARD `tenantId` = EACH `parent.tenantId`
└─ READ durable `BoardDo` KEY "top" INTO `board.top` SHARD `tenantId` = `parent.tenantId`

STAGE 2
├─ READ r2 `Bucket` KEY "banners/{parent.pid}" INTO `board.banner`
└─ SEARCH `Entry` ON durable `BoardDo` INTO `board.entries` MANY
      JOIN `parent.tenantId` = `row.tenantId` AND `parent.pid` = `row.boardId`
      SHARD `tenantId` = EACH `parent.tenantId`
